  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"ohSd5AlJ\">把基因变成四重纠缠螺旋结构，四个人每个人提供一套四分之一染色体，四套四分之一染色体互相纠缠螺旋成细胞质，然后繁育方式变成性别A将带有遗传物质的液体注入性别b，性别b将ab的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=363020597&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=2&amp;q=%E9%81%97%E4%BC%A0%E7%89%A9%E8%B4%A8&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">遗传物质<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>混合成一种流涕再注射给性别c，性别c将已有的遗传物质融合并发育成一个小肉球，再放到性别d的育儿袋里，在性别d的育儿袋里连接上新脐带，然后性别d的<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=363020597&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=3&amp;q=%E6%9F%93%E8%89%B2%E4%BD%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">染色体<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>再进入胚胎中进一步融合，经过10个月发展变成新生儿。</p><p data-pid=\"h03-7ioG\">然后，你会发现，真太慢了，受不了，人类的种群数量低到令人绝望。但是相对应的，四重奏的染色体具有更加稳定的结构，意味着细胞增值的预期数值变大，人类可以活更长的寿命了。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3e7d68273ced48e6b9513e3f06b6acc_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"519\" data-rawheight=\"508\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-1bd8afcc09f82e9c0b587058d9a8eea6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-128ed02ad17b2df8b03ff471f747177b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"519\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c3e7d68273ced48e6b9513e3f06b6acc_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-c3e7d68273ced48e6b9513e3f06b6acc_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"519\" data-rawheight=\"508\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-1bd8afcc09f82e9c0b587058d9a8eea6\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-128ed02ad17b2df8b03ff471f747177b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"519\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c3e7d68273ced48e6b9513e3f06b6acc_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3e7d68273ced48e6b9513e3f06b6acc_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"508\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
